1. Ja spasim životinju koja je bila zaglavljena u žici. (I rescue an animal that was stuck in a wire.)
2. Molim te, spas*mi me! (Please, save me!)
3. On je spasao svoju kompaniju od bankrota. (He saved his company from bankruptcy.)
4. Nadam se da ću uspeti da se spasim iz ove situacije. (I hope I will manage to save myself from this situation.)
5. Sveštenik je molio Boga da spas*i dušu preminulog. (The priest prayed to God to save the soul of the deceased.)
6. Oni su se spasavali plivajući do obale. (They were saving themselves by swimming to the shore.)
7. Doktori su uspeli da spasu pacijenta iz životne opasnosti. (Doctors managed to save the patient from life-threatening condition.)
8. Vatrogasci su brzo reagovali i spasili kuću od požara. (Firefighters reacted quickly and saved the house from fire.)